ebruary5 91\nprecious promises; that by these ye might be partakers of the divine\nnature, having escaped the corruption that is in the world through\nlust.” It is here plainly revealed that all who believe in Jesus Christ\nbecome partakers of the divine nature. Let divinity and humanity\ncooperate, and fallen human beings may be more than conquerors"
