a ready obedience to its requirements. Men\nand women must be convicted of sin before they will feel their need\nof Christ.... Those who trample under their feet the law of God have\nrejected the only means to define to the transgressor what sin is.\nThey are doing the work of the great deceiver.—The Signs of the"
