ll His dealings with\n186 ToBeLikeJesus\nhumanity. The humblest workers, in cooperation with Christ, may\ntouch chords whose vibrations shall ring to the ends of the earth and\nmake melody throughout eternal ages.—The Ministry of Healing,\n158, 159.\nUse Responsibly the Gifts of Speech and Influence, [94]"
