vine nature\nexert an influence that is Christlike. Holy angels attend them on\ntheir way, and all with whom they come in contact are helped and\nblessed. But those who do not receive Christ as their personal Savior\ncannot influence others for good.... Such lose all hope of eternal life\nthemselves, andby theirexample leadothers astray. Guardwellyour\ninfluence; it is “your reasonable service” to place it on the Lord’s"
