esus\nterize all our work, wherever we may be, whether in the kitchen, in\nthe workshop, in the office of publication, in the sanitarium, in the\ncollege, or wherever we are stationed in the vineyard of the Lord.\n“He that is faithful in that which is least is faithful also in much: and\nhe that is unjust in the least is unjust also in much.”—The Review"
