e educated in\nregard to this truth. “The harvest truly is great, but the labourers\nare few.” The teachers that shall present the truth cannot stand by\nyou to see that you do not embrace the errors that are flooding our\nland; but if you are established in the Scriptures, you will feel the\nresponsibility and will search the Scriptures for yourselves, so that"
