e spirit of the humble, and to revive\nthe heart of the contrite ones.” ...\nChrist is pleading the case of every tempted soul, but while He\nis doing this, many of His people are grieving Him by taking their\nstand with Satan to accuse their brethren and sisters, pointing to their\npolluted garments.\nLet not the criticized ones become discouraged; for while others\nare condemning them, Christ is saying of them, I have graven thee\nupon the palms of My hands. By creation and by redemption thou"
