ly\nengaging in the work of doing good to all, God’s people will exert\nan influence that will tell on all with whom they are brought in\ncontact. If those who know the truth will take hold of this work\nas opportunities are presented, day by day doing deeds of love and\nkindnessintheneighborhoodwheretheylive, Christwillberevealed"
