d that\nit is the duty of His people throughout all time to impart to others\nthe knowledge they have of the way, the life, and the truth. In all\nHis labors Jesus sought to train His church for missionary work,\nand as their numbers increased, their mission would extend, until\neventually the gospel message would belt the world through their"
