n you stand on the negative side, accusing and condemning,\nyou make room for the agencies of the power of darkness. Precious\ntime has to be spent in waging war against these agencies, because\nthere were those who refused to stand on the affirmative side....\n“Letnothingbedonethroughstrifeorvainglory.”Satanisbehind\nall strife and vainglory. Let us get out of his company, and stand\nwith those who say, “Victory is for us, and we will cling to the arm"
